Description: Ben Tre is not only memorable to visitors because of its heroic history, vast green coconut groves, but also because of its rustic and poetic natural beauty. As the first 4-star resort in Ben Tre province, coming to Ben Tre Riverside Resort, visitors will feel the peaceful space under the green coconut trees, listen to the sound of the boats breaking waves in the early morning and enjoy the cool breeze from the romantic Ham Luong River. The resort consists of 81 beautiful river view rooms, designed in harmony between modern architecture and Western river culture along with a team of professional chefs, visitors will enjoy the typical dishes of the region of Coconut, a harmonious combination of Eurasian flavors in a poetic space. In particular, the resort also has Riverside Garden- an ecological garden that specializes in serving eco-tours to visit fruit gardens, team building, meetings and outdoor parties. Enjoy and feel the difference!
